{{mbox|type=notice|text='''Notice:''' This chapter attempts to comply with the [http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Wikibooks:Neutral_point_of_view Neutral Point of View] policy. It should not be used for personal reviews, but to summarize user sentiment which occurs frequently enough to be acknowledged in general terms. If you have any doubts about what you would like to say, please start a discussion using the "Discussion" tab at the top of the page. The goal is to fairly summarize the wide range of user experience and sentiment which comes with using MagicJack. Thank you; Happy editing! {{{2|}}}}}

During its first year, [http://www.magicjack.com MagicJack] has generated strong "love it, or hate it" sentiment among customers. This topic attempts to fairly present both sides without degenerating into profuse cheerleading, nor bashing rants.

* [[/Pros/]]
* [[/Cons/]]

