[[File:Manitoba, Canada.svg|thumb|right|200px|The location of Manitoba]] Manitoba is a province of [[Wikijunior:North America/Canada|Canada]]. Manitoba is located in Western Canada and borders the U.S. states of [[Wikijunior:North America/United States/North Dakota|North Dakota]] and [[Wikijunior:North America/United States/Minnesota|Minnesota]] to the south, [[Wikijunior:North America/Canada/Nunavut|Nunavut]], [[Wikijunior:North America/Canada/The Northwest Territories|The Northwest Territories]] and Hudson Bay to the north, [[Wikijunior:North America/Canada/Saskatchewan|Saskatchewan]] to the west, and [[Wikijunior:North America/Canada/Ontario|Ontario]] to the east. Its largest and capital city is Winnipeg. [[File:Flag of Manitoba.svg|thumb|right|200px|The Flag of Manitoba]]
