[[File:Flag of Nova Scotia.svg|thumb|right|200px|The Flag of Nova Scotia]] Nova Scotia is a Canadian province located on Canada's southeastern coast.Its capital and largest city is Halifax. Nova Scotia is the second smallest province in Canada. [[File:Nova Scotia, Canada.svg|thumb|right|200px|The location of Nova Scotia]]
